                                    <list>
                                        <item>
                                            <p>Vellum, about 7 1/8 in. by 5 3/8, consisting of 56
                                                leaves. The quires, signed with letters, are six in
                                                number; and there are from 19 to 24 lines in each
                                                page.</p>
                                        </item>
